2)  program to count number of alphabets in given string
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
str=input('Enter string')
length=len(str)
count=0
for i in range(0,length):
    if(str[i].isalpha())==1:
        count=count+1 
print('No.of alphabets=',count)
------------------------------------------------
Output:
Enter string hello user
No.of alphabets= 9
